---
const title = 'Parlios — Site de vente';
---
<html lang="fr">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>{title}</title>
  </head>
  <body class="min-h-screen">
    <main class="mx-auto max-w-5xl p-8 space-y-6">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold">Parlios</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-600">Site marketing ultra rapide (Astro + îlots).</p>
      <section class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <article class="p-6 border rounded-xl">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Vitesse & SEO</h2>
          <p>Contenu statique, JS minimal, meilleures pratiques Core Web Vitals.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="p-6 border rounded-xl">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Intégrations IA</h2>
          <p>Embed d’un widget demo/assistant (îlot) sans impacter la perf globale.</p>
        </article>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
